description:
Final day! We will likely be dreading taking no rest from the day before, as we take off around the coast heading for the city of Matsuyama. After a fairly easy coastal ride with amazing views of the inland sea of Japan, we eventually turn away from Matsuyama to head to the port instead. Here we will leave the bikes before training into the city centre in order to climb up to Matsuyama Castle.

After heading back to the port, we leave via one last ferry in order to reach Hiroshima. In one final ride, we head from the port in order to reach the finish line - the Hiroshima Peace Memorial.
